keyinsights.text: For Drug A, the effective rebate  has increased by 19% in 2019 Q4 due to  Access Price Group % change  from 6.25% to 7.95% in 2018 Q1
For Drug A2,  Gross sales has increased from 10% to 12% resulting in reduction of effective rebate by 2%
For Drug A, the effective rebate by Payer 1 has increased by 19% due change in Formulary position from P -> P to P->E at the end of 17-Q4
For Drug A1, due to increased competition from Drug K in 18-Q3, ,a 1.2% higher Admin Fees and 1.0% higher Base Rebates , increased the effective rebate % by 2.2%
